Testing Samples for _E. coli_ O157:H7 and non-O157 Shiga toxin-producing _E. coli_ (EHEC): Year-to-Date Totals
-----------------------------------------------
Table 1 presents the results from analysis of raw ground beef component samples for non-O157 STECs. Results are from FSIS routine and follow-up sampling programs. Table 2 presents the results from analysis of raw ground beef component samples for both _E. coli_ O157:H7 and for the non-O157 STECs by each non-O157 STEC serogroup. Information is based upon data in the FSIS electronic data system as of 8 Jul 2012.

